Infographic: Countries which top in chauvinistic attitudes 
14-3-2017 
Countries which top in chauvinistic attitudes

Antiquated attitudes and gender stereotypes that define women as being less capable than men in performing certain tasks, such as earning money and even teaching, are still prevalent in many countries. Here’s a look at percentage of citizens of selected countries who think men are more capable than women. Sadly India’s pretty much at the top. 
